rows.name:
Why?
Why do we have to eliminate Homura?

rows.label: bf06260100_0020
rows.name: Your way of speaking is as crude as ever.

rows.label: bf06260100_0030
rows.name:
What's that got to do with anything?
Don't change the subject.

rows.label: bf06260100_0040
rows.name: What if I said justice is on my side?

rows.label: bf06260100_0060
rows.name:
You could say...
I'm doing this for Alst.
